title: The desktop does not popup with PC suite after installation
answer:
Check if PC suite and drives is installed successfully (refer to Question 2)
a. If not, replug WiMAX Stick and install again
b. If yes, click shortcut of Pc suite in【Start / All programs】
c. If part of PC suite has already been installed into PC, just uninstall it and re-plug WiMAX Stick to reinstall
